      "value": "<p><strong>Truth Earring (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 6 Gnosis.</em></p><p><strong>Effect (while worn):</strong></p><ul><li>You automatically know when a creature within 30 feet lies verbally</li><li>You gain advantage on Wisdom (Insight) checks</li></ul><p>This does not reveal the truth, only deception.</p><p>The effect lasts while you wear the earring until you deactivate it or complete a long rest.</p><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 1. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 3. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=truth-earring; rating=1; minGnosis=3; activation=action</code></p>",
